[I] Parallel Presolve for Integer and Linear Optimization

[T] PaPILO provides parallel presolve routines for (mixed integer) linear
[T] programming problems. The routines are implemented using templates which
[T] allows switching to higher precision or rational arithmetic using the boost
[T] multiprecision package.

[U] https://github.com/scipopt/papilo

[A] SCIP Project
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/development
